<div class="absoluteAlign bottomHalf blackBg">
    <h3 class="roomName">Indicator Corridor - Quantitative</h3>

    <p>A metal corridor lined with glass orbs, each filled with glowing amber fluid. The walls are digital planes abundant with light, numbers and charts flashing by too rapidly to read.</p>

    <p>The corridor runs <a class="panelOpener" identifier="north">nor��4۩</a> and [[south|indicatorCorridorQualitative]]. Steps to the [[east|glassTowerStairwell]] down to an open glass door, beyond which you can see a stairwell. A bronze slab hangs on a heavy oaken door to the [[west|diningHall]].</p>
</div>

</snippet>


<snippet name="indicatorCorridorQualitative" scripts="meta/markerDivScript.js">

<div class="absoluteAlign topHalf">
</div>
<div class="absoluteAlign bottomHalf blackBg">
    <h3 class="roomName">Indicator Corridor - Qualitative</h3>

    <p>A metal corridor lined with glass orbs, each crackling with energy. The walls are digital planes abundant with light, words in an unknown language scrolling past at breakneck pace.</p>

    <p>The corridor runs [[north|indicatorCorridorQuantitative]] and [[south|nexusDome]]. An elegant wooden door inlaid with glass and copper leads to the [[east|clockLounge]], with a <a class="whiteMarker bronzeSlab">bronze slab</a> dangling from its handle. A nondescript wooden door leads to the [[west|redLounge1]].</p>
</div>

</snippet>

<snippet name="nexusDome" scripts="meta/markerDivScript.js; meta/machineScript.js">

<div class="panelFull absoluteAlign hidden" identifier="machine">
    <p>A copper switch gleams prominently beneath a black screen.</p>

    <div class="machineScreen">
        <label for="coordinates">NODE ID</label>
        <input name="coordinates" type="number" step="1"/>
    </div>

    <p><a class="activateLink" location="nexusDome">Pull switch.</a></p>

    <div class="successfulActivation hidden">
        <p>Light flashes. A coruscating rip in the fabric of spacetime opens before you.</p>

        <p><a class="successfulActivationLink">Enter.</a></p>
    </div>
    <div class="unsuccessfulActivation hidden">
        <p>Click. Nothing happens.</p>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="absoluteAlign topHalf">
</div>
<div class="absoluteAlign bottomHalf blackBg">
    <h3 class="roomName">Nexus Dome</h3>

    <p>A dizzying range of colors filters down from a stained-glass dome, under which rests a cage-like <a class="panelOpener" identifier="machine">apparatus</a> made of interlocking bronze arms. Copper pipes and wires extend out from the base of the cage, running under the glass-topped floor into the walls.</p>

    <p>From the corridor to the [[north|indicatorCorridorQualitative]], you see flashes of amber light. A sliding glass door, behind which you can see smudges of amber and white, leads [[east|sinkhouse]]. Steam hisses from a corridor to the [[south|gearCorridor]].</p>
</div>
</snippet>


<snippet name="gearCorridor" scripts="meta/markerDivScript.js">

<div class="panelFull absoluteAlign hidden" identifier="south">
